@edsantiago do you have any idea why my test is getting permission denied when it is trying to set up a local registry? https://github.com/containers/podman/pull/21069/files#diff-c16aa2236fd1beeb5ffd9984c908f9ef18d568d372b74677837332b4ebf015b4R37.
The test failure can be found here https://github.com/containers/podman/pull/21069/checks?check_run_id=20091128750.

I am using the `start_registry` function we already have set up in the system tests that is used by some other existing tests. Could it be something with the `ROOTLESS_USER` set up I am doing to imitate a separate machine/farm node?
